{"tid":478444,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[文長慎入]又到左一年一度既中學班聚","createTime":"2017-11-24T05:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T15:29:05.000Z","uid":130162,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e28088348952b27b46df10df454c22e5638099e1","tid":478444,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"自前幾年畢業以來，每年年底都會有中學班聚會，都係例牌食晚飯，打邊爐/大排檔，仲會慶祝班主任生日<br />\n<br />\n岩岩畢業既時候，當時智能手機開始興起，於是有左whatsapp班group，起初班group好雀躍，傾近況，9up，share高登post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一有班聚會好多人岀現，大家都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而唔知從幾時開始，班group變到好靜，岀席班聚既人一年比一年少，起初畢業有大半班人，到左而家就得返幾個&hellip;whatsapp group約既話幾乎冇得人覆，然後逐個人whatsapp問，答覆都係話sorry啊唔得閒，有啲話要返工，返教會，去旅行，甚至有人話唔想應酬&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n曾經日日見面，好熟悉既同學，到後來畢業後大家都少見左好多，各自有新圈子，大家都開始岀黎社會工作，各有各忙<br />\n<br />\n記得以前岩岩升上中四既時候，好多同學都係互不相識，我個班特別多毒撚（包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），靜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後來慢慢開始熟，有啲同學讀書好好，而且好善良，會好用心咁教其他同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全班一齊為班際比賽努力，一齊比老師罰，又同班主任感情好好，打成一片，成日整鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有好多難忘既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家有時經過球場，見到班師弟妹上緊體育堂，我真係好羨慕啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好感激一直有繼續聯絡既人，多謝你地珍惜曾經有過既時光，多謝你地既重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有左whatsapp之後，隨時就可以聯絡人，但其實真正拉近人同人之間距離既唔係科技，而係人心<br />\n<br />\n五年之後，唔知我地又會變成點呢？"},{"pid":"fe9a0a874e4317453e5995750c901da6e8f1b03e","tid":478444,"uid":75154,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:25:25.000Z","msg":"講經咩"},{"pid":"3da82c6e1e4dbb133972ed937b079bd1486ceb76","tid":478444,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2741f63b8c30a0726d860f644c90c65554ee0629","tid":478444,"uid":130365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"天下没有不散的筵席<br />\n時間一長 ， 感情點都會沖淡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e5f86f4397db5772c75a14b1b43af7d8257e9a","tid":478444,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a15ebf93b036001c494bc2eb8e14eee6d8c8da8","tid":478444,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"5年後可能last果幾個都結哂婚 有自己頭家。 重邊得閒理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a20c131ceb67fdd7a06ded6b54dab5b799c517","tid":478444,"uid":100230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"中學有最熟既一班fd就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92903b1c06f2b84aa103df480b3e1ef87dcbab90","tid":478444,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學有最熟既一班fd就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8abd161ab4a6b9ee84e4d8f5135ff728d9c9c3a","tid":478444,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天下没有不散的筵席<br />\n時間一長 ， 感情點都會沖淡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾經感情好好既人，而家好似陌生人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffde52fff900cb643c64f7c4f27928fd2ce1c2a7","tid":478444,"uid":27509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"係咁嫁啦"},{"pid":"e0b9a50900aa117055fecdeb08677d040568f7a7","tid":478444,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5年後可能last果幾個都結哂婚 有自己頭家。 重邊得閒理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一年見到一次，間中whatsapp下已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e0d94a42e02e62ca06a296569fd455471ea939","tid":478444,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"有人叫你去咪算係咁囉"},{"pid":"a873a6688f37d5cb3c5dfc50b96fd0b8a48b57c8","tid":478444,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人叫你去咪算係咁囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真，做搞手係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}